A exhausted figure slumped over a cluttered desk at 3am, surrounded by towering stacks of crumpled papers and empty coffee cups, their face illuminated by the harsh blue glow of multiple computer monitors displaying endless lines of code. The scene is rendered in bold comic book style with heavy ink lines, dramatic shadows, and halftone dot patterns. A wall calendar behind them shows days aggressively crossed out in red, with the final visible date circled multiple times. Steam rises from a cold, forgotten coffee mug. The figure's posture conveys complete defeat—head in hands, shoulders hunched. Through a window, a weekend sunrise mockingly peeks through blinds, suggesting yet another lost day off. The color palette emphasizes exhaustion: muted blues, harsh yellows from the screens, and deep shadows contrasting with angry red accents on the calendar marks.
